HEAT olive oil in large saucepan over medium-high heat. Add garlic. COOK, stirring occasionally for 1 minute. Add broth, water and Italian seasoning; bring to a boil. Add pasta and carrot; reduce heat to medium. COOK, stirring occasionally, for 8 minutes. Stir in spinach. COOK for 1 to 2 minutes or until wilted. SERVE immediately. Sprinkle with Parmesan cheese and freshly ground black pepper, if desired.